high_descs: Turn around and walk to the blue waste bin.
Grab the pink spray bottle that is in the blue waste bin.
Turn to the toilet to your right.
Place the pink spray bottle on top of the toilet tank.
Turn left and walk to the bathroom vanity.
Pick up the pink spray bottle on top of the bathroom vanity.
Turn right and walk to the toilet.
Put the pink spray bottle on top of the toilet tank and to the right of the other pink spray bottle.
anns.task_desc: Put two pink spray bottles on the toilet tank.

high_descs: turn around and walk over to the blue garbage bin to the left of the toilet
grab the spray bottle out of the garbage bin
back up a bit and face the top of the toilet
place the spray bottle on top of the toilet
turn left and walk over to the bathroom sink counter on the right
grab the spray bottle off of the bathroom sink counter
turn right and walk back over to the blue garbage bin on the left
place the spray bottle on top of the toilet to the right of the garbage bin
anns.task_desc: place two spray bottles on top of the toilet

high_descs: Turn around and go to the trash can.
Pick up the spray bottle from the trash can.
Look up at the toilet tank.
Put the bottle on the toilet tank.
Move to the counter on your left.
Pick up the spray bottle from the counter.
Return to the toilet.
Put the bottle on the toilet tank.
anns.task_desc: Put both spray bottles on the toilet tank.

high_descs: Turn around, walk to the trashcan.
Pick up the purple spray bottle. that is in the trashcan.
Walk closer to the toilet.
Put the purple spray bottle next to the toilet paper on top of the toilet tank.
Turn left, walk to the end of the counter.
Pick up the purple spray bottle.
Walk back to the toilet.
Put the spray bottle next to the first spray bottle.
anns.task_desc: Put the two purple spray bottles on the toilet tank.
